FuncDef: The undo acl name command deletes a created ACL. The undo acl name command deletes a created ACL. By default, no ACL is created.

ParaDef.Info:
Creates an ACL with a name.
The value is a string of 1 to 32 case-sensitive characters, spaces not supported.

ExtraInfo: To delete an existing ACL, run the undo acl command.
